title: Stanford CS230 | Autumn 2025 | Lecture 10: What’s Going On Inside My Model?
description:
For more information about Stanford’s Artificial Intelligence professional and graduate programs, visit: https://stanford.io/ai

December 2, 2025
This lecture covers what's happening inside your model and provides a class wrap-up.

To learn more about enrolling in this course, visit: https://online.stanford.edu/courses/cs230-deep-learning

Please follow along with the course schedule and syllabus: https://cs230.stanford.edu/syllabus/

View the playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLoROMvodv4rNRRGdS0rBbXOUGA0wjdh1X
